If any of the afore mentioned packaging modes does not suite your needs you may use the [Installer plugin|http://griffon.codehaus.org/Installer+Plugin] to craft a better packaging option. This plugin supports the following additional modes:

* @izpack@ - universal installer using [Izpack|http://izpack.org].
* @dmg@ - for MacOSX.
* @rpm@ - for RPM based Linux distributions.
* @jsmooth@ - for Windows.